    - Term: Conversation/0x0100003100005E11/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - "Talk to Cunoesse to find out she's a girl.\n \n \"I have nothing interesting say, talk to Cuno!\"\n \n Or approach her from the backyard to catch her off-guard and have something-resembling an actual dialogue with her."
      Flags: 00
